results.name: Signature permutation of a Catalan bijection: row 3656 of A089840.
comment: This bijection of binary trees is obtained in the following way. See also comments at A154122.
That is, we do (a . (b . (c . d))) -> (a . ((b . c) . d))
or (a . (b . ())) --> (b . (() . a)) if the former is not possible.
Note that the first clause corresponds to generator B of Thompson's groups F, T and V. See further comments at A154121.
reference: J. W. Cannon, W. J. Floyd and W. R. Parry, Introductory notes on Richard Thompson's groups, L'Enseignement Mathematique, Vol. 42 (1996), pp. 215--256.
